==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wintry
<hw>Win"try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>wintrig</ets>.]</ety> <def>Suitable to winter; resembling winter,
or what belongs to winter; brumal; hyemal; cold; stormy;
wintery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Touch our chilled hearts with vernal smile,⟦br⟧
Our <qex>wintry</qex> course do thou beguile.</q>
<rj><qau>Keble.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Winy</ent>⟦br⟧
